Generic single-database configuration for Alembic migrations.

## Quick Start

### Create a new migration
```bash
alembic revision --autogenerate -m "description of changes"
```

### Apply migrations
```bash
alembic upgrade head
```

### Downgrade migrations
```bash
alembic downgrade -1  # Go back one revision
alembic downgrade base  # Go back to the beginning
```

### View migration history
```bash
alembic history
alembic current
```

## Directory Structure

- `env.py` - Alembic environment configuration
- `script.py.mako` - Template for generating migration scripts
- `versions/` - Directory containing migration scripts (auto-generated)

